{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/Operations/24-06-22/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>AWS Lambda, AWS SQS를 통해 이벤트를 전달 받고, 특정 이벤트에 대한 경고 알림을 slack으로 전송하는 방법에 대해서 기록합니다. Lambda 개발은 vscode의 AWS Toolkit을 활용하였고, slack 알림은 slack webhook bot을 활용하였습니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"aws-serverless-application-model-sam\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#aws-serverless-application-model-sam\" aria-label=\"aws serverless application model sam permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AWS Serverless Application Model (SAM)</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>AWS SAM CLI 설치: <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/serverless-application-model/latest/developerguide/install-sam-cli.html\">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/serverless-application-model/latest/developerguide/install-sam-cli.html</a></li>\n<li>VScode AWS Toolkit plugin 설치</li>\n<li>VScode AWS Toolkit에서 AWS 로그인</li>\n<li>Lambda 항목을 우클릭 후 Create Lambda SAM Application</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">lambda_handler</code> function 안에 코드 작성</li>\n<li>Build: requirements에 필요 패키지 작성 후 <code class=\"language-text\">sam build</code> 명령어 통해 이미지 빌드. 패키지 설치 필요없는 경우에는 <code class=\"language-text\">-—skip-pull-image</code> 옵션 통해 image pull 스킵가능. <code class=\"language-text\">sam build</code> 명령 사용하면 <code class=\"language-text\">.aws-sam</code> 폴더 생김</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sam build (--skip-pull-image)</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>Test(invoke): <code class=\"language-text\">event.json</code>에 예시 event 작성 후, 로컬 lambda function을 테스트 해볼 수 있음. 함수 테스트 전에는 변경된 함수 적용 위해 build 필요. <code class=\"language-text\">sam local start-api</code> 명령어 사용하면 <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:3000\">http://127.0.0.1:3000</a> 서버 형태로 실행되어서 postman 통한 디버깅도 가능</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sam local invoke -e events/event.json\n\n# If you have an error when finding docker, run command below\nDOCKER_HOST=unix://$HOME/.docker/run/docker.sock sam local invoke -e events/event.json</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/4fa52/24-06-21-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.105263157894738%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAd0lEQVQI1z3Myw7CIBCF4b4GxEKGqzZFQU2w0Or7P9VRZuHiy0zO4p/qq2JvB/q2416eKPmBNWWkdMPlvMAaB28DSBvMJwU1a2itoZRi45dSQgjBpt46tto4OMLD+/ggXwvWJcFZz0HvAgwZvjFGhPDbvGdE9PcFulg7HcYSaagAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/15813/24-06-21-1.webp 190w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/1cdb2/24-06-21-1.webp 380w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/9046c/24-06-21-1.webp 760w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/c89f9/24-06-21-1.webp 1140w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/67580/24-06-21-1.webp 1241w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/a2d4f/24-06-21-1.png 190w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/3f520/24-06-21-1.png 380w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/3c051/24-06-21-1.png 760w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/b5cea/24-06-21-1.png 1140w,\n/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/4fa52/24-06-21-1.png 1241w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ae00b8ea25531f3256d69723b0c3b50c/3c051/24-06-21-1.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"img\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>Deployment: 배포를 위한 설정은 <code class=\"language-text\">template.yaml</code> 파일에서 가능</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sam deploy # 최초 배포시 --guided 옵션 추가</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li>Lambda를 테스트하기 위한 테스트 이벤트는 <a href=\"https://github.com/aws/aws-lambda-go/tree/main/events/testdata\">이곳</a>에서 참고 가능</li>\n<li>\n<p>Role 설정 필요. <a href=\"https://devblog.kakaostyle.com/ko/2017-05-13-1-aws-serverless-1/\">kakao style의 테크 블로그</a> 참고</p>\n<ul>\n<li>SQS 관련 필요 권한: <code class=\"language-text\">sqs:ReceiveMessage</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">sqs:DeleteMessage</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">sqs:GetQueueAttributes</code></li>\n<li>Lambda 관련 필요 권한: <code class=\"language-text\">lambda:InvokeFunction</code></li>\n<li>CloudWatch 관련 필요 권한: <code class=\"language-text\">logs:CreateLogGroup</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">logs:CreateLogStream</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">logs:PutLogEvents</code></li>\n<li>만약 S3 권한 필요시 AmazonS3FullAccess 같은 role 부여</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"slack-webhook-bot\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#slack-webhook-bot\" aria-label=\"slack webhook bot permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Slack Webhook Bot</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Slack App을 생성한 뒤, 'Incoming Webhooks' section에서 'Activate Incoming Webhooks'을 On 설정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>WebHook?: <a href=\"https://docs.tosspayments.com/resources/glossary/webhook\">https://docs.tosspayments.com/resources/glossary/webhook</a></li>\n<li>클라이언트가 서버를 호출하는게 아닌, 서버에 특정 이벤트가 발생했을 때 클라이언트를 호출하기 때문에 '역방향 API'라고도 불림</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>'Incoming Webhooks' section에서 'Add New Webhook to Workspace'를 통해 Webhook 사용할 채널 추가</li>\n<li>생성된 Webhook URL 확인 및 복사</li>\n<li>curl 통해서 잘 작동하는지 테스트. 그리고 Lambda 내에서 해당 Webhook url 활용</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">curl -s -d &quot;payload={&#39;text&#39;:&#39;hello world&#39;}&quot; &quot;YOUR_WEBHOOK_URL&quot;</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 627px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/e9c9b/24-06-21-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.78947368421053%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/15813/24-06-21-2.webp 190w,\n/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/1cdb2/24-06-21-2.webp 380w,\n/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/c4111/24-06-21-2.webp 627w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 627px) 100vw, 627px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/a2d4f/24-06-21-2.png 190w,\n/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/3f520/24-06-21-2.png 380w,\n/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/e9c9b/24-06-21-2.png 627w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 627px) 100vw, 627px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d6e32375f7cdb1f458970aed6f346527/e9c9b/24-06-21-2.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"img\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"aws-simple-queue-service-sqs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#aws-simple-queue-service-sqs\" aria-label=\"aws simple queue service sqs permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AWS Simple Queue Service (SQS)</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>AWS SQS를 생성 및 액세스 정책 설정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>특정 서비스(e.g., S3)에 SNS 걸어두고 해당 SNS를 SQS가 구독하는 형태가 일반적</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>생성한 SQS의 Lambda 트리거로, 위에서 만든 Lambda를 설정</li>\n<li>저장 후 결과 확인</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/53639/24-06-21-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.47368421052632%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/15813/24-06-21-3.webp 190w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/1cdb2/24-06-21-3.webp 380w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/9046c/24-06-21-3.webp 760w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/c89f9/24-06-21-3.webp 1140w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/6ae26/24-06-21-3.webp 1358w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/a2d4f/24-06-21-3.png 190w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/3f520/24-06-21-3.png 380w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/3c051/24-06-21-3.png 760w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/b5cea/24-06-21-3.png 1140w,\n/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/53639/24-06-21-3.png 1358w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d3f933c4d61ce2217b2cdd1e7a9c34e6/3c051/24-06-21-3.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"img\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Message를 직접 확인하고싶은 경우, SQS의 '메세지 전송 및 수신'에 들어가서 메세지를 직접 폴링해보고 결과를 확인해볼 수 있음</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"summary\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#summary\" aria-label=\"summary permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Summary</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>특정 이벤트 발생 (e.g., SNS)</li>\n<li>SQS를 통해 이벤트가 Lambda로 전달</li>\n<li>해당 이벤트에 대해 alert 필요한지를 Lambda 내 lambda_handler에서 확인</li>\n<li>Alert 필요한 경우, slack webhook url로 message 전송</li>\n<li>Slack 채널에서 alert 확인</li>\n</ol>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/MachineLearning/24-06-22-Alert%20System%20with%20SQS,%20Lambda,%20and%20Slack/#aws-serverless-application-model-sam\">AWS Serverless Application Model (SAM)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/MachineLearning/24-06-22-Alert%20System%20with%20SQS,%20Lambda,%20and%20Slack/#slack-webhook-bot\">Slack Webhook Bot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/MachineLearning/24-06-22-Alert%20System%20with%20SQS,%20Lambda,%20and%20Slack/#aws-simple-queue-service-sqs\">AWS Simple Queue Service (SQS)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/MachineLearning/24-06-22-Alert%20System%20with%20SQS,%20Lambda,%20and%20Slack/#summary\">Summary</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/Operations/24-06-22/","title":"Alert System with SQS, Lambda, and Slack","category":"Operations","date":"2024-06-22"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["2390655019","256249292","63159454"]}